title: Fresh Herb Bread Machine Bread
ingredients: ['150ml milk', '2 eggs', '410g bread flour', '1 1/2 teaspoons salt', '2 1/2 tablespoons caster sugar', '1 teaspoon chopped fresh rosemary', '1 teaspoon chopped fresh thyme', '1 teaspoon dried marjoram', '1 1/2 tablespoons margarine', '2 teaspoons dried active yeast']
